<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="cry-out">cry out</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>(因害怕、震惊、疼痛等) 大声叫喊：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She <strong>cried out in / with</strong> pain when her tooth was pulled out.
她拔牙时痛得大叫。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>“Why are you doing this?”she cried out suddenly.
“你为什么要这么做？”她突然大声喊道。</p></div></div>